'''蘇爾吉特·辛格·巴爾納拉'''（{{lang-hi|सुरजीत सिंह बरनाला}}；{{bd|1925年|10月21日|2017年|1月14日|catIdx=Barnala}}），[[印度|印度]]政治人物，曾任[[旁遮普邦|旁遮普邦]]{{le|旁遮普邦首席部長 (印度)|List of Chief Ministers of Punjab (India)|首席部長}}；[[泰米尔纳德邦|泰米尔纳德邦]]、[[北阿坎德邦|北阿坎德邦]]、[[安得拉邦|安得拉邦]]與[[安达曼-尼科巴群岛|安达曼-尼科巴群岛]]{{le|印度各邦總督|Governors of states of India|總督}}與不同職務的{{le|聯邦委員會部長|Union Council of Ministers|聯邦部長}}<ref name="Death">{{cite web |url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/former-punjab-chief-minister-surjit-singh-barnala-passes-away-aged-91/articleshow/56538368.cms |title=Former Punjab Chief Minister Surjit Singh Barnala passes away, aged 91 |work=Times of India |date=14 January 2017 |accessdate=17 January 2017 |archive-date=2017-01-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170116195721/http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/former-punjab-chief-minister-surjit-singh-barnala-passes-away-aged-91/articleshow/56538368.cms |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

巴爾納拉也是一名畫家，主要繪畫風景和政治肖像，其中許多作品都在他任職時的官邸展出，也賣出部分畫作為各種基金募款<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.hindu.com/2006/04/05/stories/2006040519150400.htm |title=Painting for charity |access-date=2017-01-18 |archive-date=2007-10-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071001090709/http://www.hindu.com/2006/04/05/stories/2006040519150400.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="paint">{{cite web|url=http://www.thehindu.com/2005/04/15/stories/2005041514490300.htm |title=A brush with the Governor |author=T.S. Shankar |work=The Hindu |date=15 April 2005 |accessdate=17 January 2017}}</ref>。

==個人生活==
蘇爾吉特·辛格·巴爾納拉與同為政治人物的{{le|蘇爾吉特·考爾·巴爾納拉|Surjit Kaur Barnala}}（Surjit Kaur Barnala）結婚；2009年考爾·巴爾納拉成為{{le|最高阿卡利黨（阿姆利則）|Shiromani Akali Dal (Longowal)}}的黨主席<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.tribuneindia.com/2009/20090821/punjab.htm#4 |title=Barnala family revives SAD (L) |author=Goyal, Sushil |date=21 August 2009 |work=Tribune India |accessdate=17 January 2017 |archive-date=2019-06-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190616215628/https://www.tribuneindia.com/2009/20090821/punjab.htm#4 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。二人共有三名兒子和一名女兒，次子{{le|軋根吉·辛格·巴爾納拉|Gaganjit Singh Barnala}}亦從事政治活動，而幼子和女兒分別在1996年及2012年死於車禍和癌症<ref name="DeathHindu">{{cite web |url=http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/Surjit-Singh-Barnala-passes-away/article17040243.ece |title=Surjit Singh Barnala passes away |work=The Hindu |date=14 January 2017 |accessdate=17 January 2017 |archive-date=2017-01-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170115173831/http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/Surjit-Singh-Barnala-passes-away/article17040243.ece |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==逝世==
2017年1月12日巴爾納拉被送入[[昌迪加尔|昌迪加尔]]的{{le|研究生醫學教育研究所|Postgraduate Institute of Medical Education and Research}}，到14日因長期患病逝世<ref name="Death"/>。

